      <a href="matlab:web('C:\Program Files\MATLAB\R2024b\help/matlab/ref/eig.html#btgapg5-1-D')">D</a> - Eigenvalues (returned as matrix)
        diagonal matrix
      <a href="matlab:web('C:\Program Files\MATLAB\R2024b\help/matlab/ref/eig.html#btgapg5-1-W')">W</a> - Left eigenvectors
        square matrix

